mountpoint (eg. \f(CW\*(C`/boot\*(C'\fR) and a value which is the filesystem that would be
mounted there (eg. \f(CW\*(C`/dev/sda1\*(C'\fR).
.PP
Non-mounted devices such as swap devices are \fInot\fR returned in this list.
.PP
