will only return an entry for the first drive \*(L"mounted on\*(R" \f(CW\*(C`/\*(C'\fR.  For
information about the mapping of drive letters to partitions, see
\&\f(CW\*(C`guestfs_inspect_get_drive_mappings\*(C'\fR.
